LineEditor_ReadInfo
#Parent LineEditor_
=>	R0 =	taskhandle of taskwindow to find info for
<=	R0 =	length of line currently being edited in that taskwindow,
	 	or -2 if that is not a known task,
	 	or -1 if that is a known task but no edit is in progress
	R1 =	cursor position

This SWI is used to read information about the LineEditor edits in progress.
